{"article_id":"2rr9MWivGQHZxlEj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Judiciary Chair Chuck Grassley","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"( R-IA )","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"has rescheduled a committee vote on Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh for this upcoming Friday .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"That ' s just one day after a hearing","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"that will take place on Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"which is set","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"to scrutinize sexual misconduct and assault allegations","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that have been brought against Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Grassley ' s announcement of the committee vote is the latest signal","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that Republicans are ready to barrel ahead with Kavanaugh ' s confirmation ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"in spite of the recent accusations","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that have been levied by Christine Blasey Ford and Deborah Ramirez .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Ford","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"who has said","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"that Kavanaugh tried to force himself on her","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"while both of them were in high school -","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"is set to testify , along with Kavanaugh , on Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Kavanaugh has unequivocally denied all of the allegations .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell on Tuesday emphasized","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that he was eager to hear from Ford","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"- while simultaneously casting doubt on the legitimacy of her allegations .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"\" The American people ... insist","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that vague , unsubstantiated , and uncorroborated allegations of 30-plus-year-old misconduct","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"- where all the supposed witnesses either totally deny it","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"or can ' t confirm it -","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"is nowhere near grounds","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to nullify someone ' s career or destroy their good name , \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"McConnell said in floor remarks .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"A Grassley spokesperson said","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"that the announcement of the vote was simply a procedural move","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"in case the committee stands ready to advance Kavanaugh right after Thursday ' s hearing .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"\" Committee rules normally require executive business meetings to be noticed three days in advance ,","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"so an executive business meeting is being noticed tonight","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"in the event","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"that a majority of the members are prepared to hold one on Friday , \"","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"the spokesperson said in a statement .","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"Republicans have an 11-10 majority in the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":3},{"id":38,"text":"which sets Kavanaugh up for a likely positive recommendation from the panel .","depth":3},{"id":39,"text":"Of the Republicans , Sen. Jeff Flake","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"( R-AZ )","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"is the only one","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"who ' s given any indication","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"that he could potentially flip and oppose the nomination .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Flake has previously said","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"he wouldn ' t vote on Kavanaugh ' s nomination","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"until he had heard from Ford .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"His vote , like those of a number of other lawmakers , could come down to her testimony on Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"\" Obviously ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"if you believe","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"the charges are true ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"then you vote no , \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Flake has said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":105,"left":89,"right":104,"relation":"e